      <title>交易员权衡盈利和政策前景，欧洲股市稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市几乎没有变化，因为投资者正在处理源源不断的财报和央行官员热衷于缓和早期降息希望的消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sainsbury’s 承诺节省 10 亿英镑并回购股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/sainsbury-s-pledges-1-billion-savings-and-200-million-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[J Sainsbury Plc 计划削减 10 亿英镑（12 亿美元）成本并回购股票，作为更新战略的一部分，该战略有望加强连锁超市对食品销售的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/sainsbury-s-pledges-1-billion-savings-and-200-million-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:41:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orsted 削减股息，首席执行官试图削减不断上升的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Orsted A/S 将暂停支付股息，至少到 2025 年为止，并削减本十年建设新项目的计划，作为首席执行官 Mads Nipper 概述的一系列成本削减措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维斯塔斯表示，随着危机缓解，今年的前景正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 预计，随着这家丹麦公司扭转了导致项目开发放缓的全行业危机，在 2023 年恢复盈利后，今年的盈利将有所改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
